# Summary
This documentation page details the Amazon Kinesis Firehose destination integration for Amplitude Data, explaining how to stream Amplitude event data to Kinesis Firehose by creating an AWS IAM role with specific permissions, setting up a Firehose stream, and configuring the connection in Amplitude's destination catalog.

